Annual Gala: Sweet Beginnings Tea

Since 2005, we have celebrated our community with a very special event: our annual Sweet Beginnings Tea. Each February, we come together to reflect on our history, and raise funds for our future.

SWEET BEGINNINGS TEA

A tradition of giving.

The Sweet Beginnings Tea is NLEN's largest annual fundraising event, playing a crucial role in supporting our mission. It began in earnest in 2005 as a small fundraiser to celebrate the newly launched Sweet Beginnings, LLC, social enterprise business.

Now in its 20th year, NLEN’s Sweet Beginnings Tea raises unrestricted funds that are vital for our programs and services, empowering us to address the most pressing needs of the North Lawndale community.

Support our next Sweet Beginnings Tea

Thank you for joining us at the 20th Annual Sweet Beginnings Tea!

The event was a massive success thanks to all of our amazing supporters. We cannot wait to see you at the rest of our 25th anniversary events and next year's Tea!
